plan.name: rc1-nftfactory-v1
plan.info: Add x/nftfactory store key (permissionless class creation + admin-only mint into x/nft)

title: RC1: Enable NFTFactory (native NFTs)
summary: Adds the x/nftfactory store key via the rc1-nftfactory-v1 upgrade so users can permissionlessly create native NFT classes (nft/<creator>/<sub_id>) and mint NFTs (admin-only) backed by the chain's x/nft module.
